  "name": "Building Blocks - OGC API Common",
  "abstract": "Schemas for the OGC API - Common - Part 1: Core standard\n",
  "description": "Adds a flexible, JSON schema version agnostic documentation to the OGC API - Common - Part 1: Core standard, \nsupporting further profiling by combining with other Building Blocks.\n\nThis includes:\n- Landing Page (/)\n- Conformance Declaration (/conformance)\n- API Definition (/api)\n- Common response formats (JSON, HTML)\n- Common schemas (links, exceptions, etc.)\n",
  "modified": "2026-06-11T16:35:57.951701",
